{"id":171,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":171,"title":"2 Corinthians 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Saints should test themselves as to righteousness—Be perfect and of one mind; live in peace."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.1","order":"03.10.013.19295"},["b","1"],"This",["i","is"],"the third",["i","time"],"I am coming to you. In the mouth of two or three",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"witnesses"],"shall every word be established."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.2","order":"03.10.013.19296"},["b","2"],"I told you before, and foretell you, as if I were present, the second time; and being absent now I write to them which heretofore have sinned, and to all other, that, if I come again, I will not spare:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.3","order":"03.10.013.19297"},["b","3"],"Since ye seek a proof of Christ speaking in me, which to you-ward is not weak, but is mighty in you."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.4","order":"03.10.013.19298"},["b","4"],"For though he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"crucified"],"through weakness, yet he liveth by the power of God. For we also are weak in him, but we shall live with him by the power of God toward you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.5","order":"03.10.013.19299"},["b","5"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Examine"],"yourselves, whether ye be in the faith; prove your own selves. Know ye not your own selves, how that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Jesus"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Christ"],"is in you, except ye be reprobates?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.6","order":"03.10.013.19300"},["b","6"],"But I trust that ye shall know that we are not reprobates."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.7","order":"03.10.013.19301"},["b","7"],"Now I pray to God that ye do no evil; not that we should appear approved, but that ye should do that which is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"honest"],", though we be as reprobates."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.8","order":"03.10.013.19302"},["b","8"],"For we can do nothing against the truth, but for the truth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.9","order":"03.10.013.19303"},["b","9"],"For we are glad, when we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"weak"],", and ye are strong: and this also we wish,",["i","even"],"your perfection."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.10","order":"03.10.013.19304"},["b","10"],"Therefore I write these things being absent, lest being present I should use sharpness, according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"power"],"which the Lord hath given me to edification, and not to destruction."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11","order":"03.10.013.19305"},["b","11"],"Finally, brethren, farewell. Be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"perfect"],", be of good comfort, be of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"one"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"mind"],", live in",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"peace"],"; and the God of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"love"],"and peace shall be with you."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.12","order":"03.10.013.19306"},["b","12"],"Greet one another with an holy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"kiss"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.13","order":"03.10.013.19307"},["b","13"],"All the saints salute you."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.14","order":"03.10.013.19308"},["b","14"],"The grace of the Lord Jesus Christ, and the love of God, and the communion of the Holy Ghost,",["i","be"],"with you all. Amen."]],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor.closing.3","order":".000.19337"},[".closing","¶The second",["i","epistle"],"to the Corinthians was written from Philippi,",["i","a city"],"of Macedonia, by Titus and Lucas."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.1a","order":"03.10.013.19309"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.15"},"Deut. 19:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.28"},"D&C 6:28"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.4a","order":"03.10.013.19311"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.5a","order":"03.10.013.19313"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/11.28.27-31"},"1 Cor. 11:28 (27–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.5b","order":"03.10.013.19315"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.24.19-24"},"1 Jn. 3:24 (19–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/4.12.7-21"},"4:12 (7–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.5c","order":"03.10.013.19317"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.10"},"Rom. 8:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.7a","order":"03.10.013.19319"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.9a","order":"03.10.013.19321"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9"},"2 Cor. 12:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.10a","order":"03.10.013.19323"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.8"},"2 Cor. 10:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11a","order":"03.10.013.19325"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11b","order":"03.10.013.19327"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11c","order":"03.10.013.19329"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.10.10-13"},"1 Cor. 1:10 (10–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11d","order":"03.10.013.19331"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"11e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.11e","order":"03.10.013.19333"},["b","11e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.12a","order":"03.10.013.19335"},["b","12a"],["span.small","JST"],"2 Cor. 13:12 …",["i","salutation."]]]}
